channel.description:
Well, I think considering this has been my first server, I've done really well so far. But I'm having trouble with DClaw Specials, Lunar Interface and PVP Armour.. Maybe I'm just sick of coding today, but I don't think so. I don't want this to turn into a flame thread and nor do i expect to be spoon fed. Just hoping for someone to lead me to some tutorials, as I've had no luck searching.
Thanks !
